# Format: module | module:rule | *:rule | module:rule@glob | path/**

# HomeEyesEarsHands renders marketing code snippets inside template literals.
# The localhost URLs are display text for customers, not endpoints this app
# calls — and a suppressor comment inside the template would render on the
# page. Scoped to this one file only.
