# reliability-corpus/ is the INTENTIONAL known-bad code corpus the flywheel
# trainers learn from. Findings in it are the corpus working as designed,
# not defects in GateTest — counting them against the self-scan would be
# self-deception in the other direction.
reliability-corpus/**

